Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.93,0:00:05.48,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(290,260)\fad(600,600)\bord15\shad0\be30\3a&H50\3c&HFFFFFF&}好\N夏
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.67,0:00:19.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀  好熱好熱  熱死了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.37,0:00:24.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,田中君你從剛才開始就只在說「好熱」哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.76,0:00:26.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來就很熱了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.39,0:00:28.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再說「好熱」就會更加熱了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.11,0:00:30.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准你說「好熱」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.20,0:00:32.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK  OK
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.85,0:00:36.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀  好夏  好夏
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.96,0:00:39.22,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}這裡田中是故意把夏天好熱「なつはあつい」說成熱天好夏「あつはなつい」\N在日本是這是著名的大叔冷笑話。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.96,0:00:39.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熱天好夏呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.38,0:00:40.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開個玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.79,0:00:42.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是真的很夏
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.76,0:00:44.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏過頭了啊  好夏
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.93,0:00:46.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好夏好夏
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.53,0:00:48.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只想打這傢伙一頓
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.07,0:00:51.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀  好夏  真夏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.71,0:00:53.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的好夏！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.05,0:00:00.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.36,0:02:27.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shining
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.15,0:02:31.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天所有的一切看上去都如此耀眼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.98,0:02:34.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空氣也好  人也好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.96,0:02:37.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且就連這間教室也好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.80,0:02:39.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是因為
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.65,0:02:44.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我今天做了作業啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.18,0:02:48.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向美緒炫耀一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.23,0:02:54.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.14,0:02:56.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧咧？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.34,0:03:01.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧咧咧咧…咧…咧…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.74,0:03:01.13,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(70,300)\fad(400,600)}日\N常\N之\N48
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.55,0:03:06.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒帶！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.50,0:03:08.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不不  怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.66,0:03:11.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明明好不容易而且如此難得地做了作業
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.30,0:03:12.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼  為什麼為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.05,0:03:14.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼沒有帶啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.11,0:03:18.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛  讓別人給我看看就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.36,0:03:19.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美緒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.69,0:03:22.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.18,0:03:25.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  等等啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.71,0:03:28.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的作業是印刷紙啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.04,0:03:37.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼了祐子  大清早地就…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.01,0:03:40.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作業忘記（帶）了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.89,0:03:44.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迷之外星人大侵略
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.74,0:03:46.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又忘記（做）了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.74,0:03:49.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要輕視我！  我明明有做  只是忘記帶了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.81,0:03:51.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀  我沒有輕視你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.88,0:03:54.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說的作業是國語的印刷紙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.27,0:03:56.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許是夾在某個地方了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.93,0:03:57.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好好地找下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.85,0:04:01.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我剛才就翻了好幾遍了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.63,0:04:03.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對已經…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.85,0:04:09.89,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}街道會  大福展銷會
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.99,0:04:11.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My  god！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.16,0:04:14.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大福展銷會是什麼啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.63,0:04:17.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛  展銷會什麼的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.61,0:04:18.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.23,0:04:20.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看  祐子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.47,0:04:23.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到講臺找找的話  也許還有剩餘的印刷紙哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.18,0:04:28.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧不是吧  還有嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.47,0:04:32.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.99,0:04:36.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡可惡  真可惡！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.03,0:04:39.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要回去拿嗎  趕不上的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.03,0:04:45.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使那樣我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.85,0:04:46.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去拿！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.40,0:04:55.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  課要開始了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.05,0:04:57.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回到座位上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.20,0:00:00.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.13,0:05:44.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咕嚕咕嚕咕嚕咕嚕…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.36,0:05:46.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轉啊轉  轉啊轉…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.73,0:05:49.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要快就轉它
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.73,0:05:49.04,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}急がば回れ原意是欲速則不達，此處借用其表面意思
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.20,0:00:00.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.43,0:05:51.90,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(290,300)\fad(600,0)}日\N常\N之\N49
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.06,0:05:53.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又被罵了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.45,0:05:58.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼總是像這樣每次每次把作業忘記呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.85,0:06:01.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天居然是明明做了卻又忘在了家裡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.86,0:06:03.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上天還真是壞心眼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.20,0:00:00.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.58,0:06:30.68,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(290,250)\fad(600,600)\bord15\shad0\be30\3a&H50\3c&HFFFFFF&}名\N片
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.49,0:06:30.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阪本
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.95,0:06:34.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請收下我的名片
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.39,0:06:39.41,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}博士
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.04,0:06:39.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼  我該怎樣才好…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.17,0:06:43.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.34,0:06:47.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我該怎麼辦才好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.20,0:00:00.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.75,0:06:53.85,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(620,320)\fad(600,600)\bord15\shad0\be30\3a&H50\3c&HFFFFFF&}自\N動\N售\N貨\N機
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.40,0:07:04.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  對不…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.77,0:07:09.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼了  立花美里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.95,0:07:11.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.08,0:07:16.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為出新品了啊  我只是在猶豫該買哪一個
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.64,0:07:18.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.14,0:07:19.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼這邊的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.99,0:07:22.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼可能會聽你的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.47,0:07:26.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…飲料很難喝  選旁邊的可能會好些哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.09,0:07:31.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.57,0:07:42.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不是聽從你的推薦才買的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.20,0:00:00.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.14,0:08:02.62,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(650,300)\fad(400,600)}日\N常\N之\N50
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.69,0:08:02.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說附近有攤子擺出來了  我決定去看一看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.34,0:08:05.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的目的就是去玩打靶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.12,0:08:09.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我只在電視上看到過  所以今天非常期待
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.40,0:08:14.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然如此  我只帶了500円  沒問題吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.91,0:08:16.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  一次500萬円
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.94,0:08:18.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lucky  剛好500円
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.39,0:08:23.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然也想吃炒麵  但是今天是為這個而來的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.85,0:08:31.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獎品只有奶糖和茄子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.46,0:08:36.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  只有這些東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.75,0:08:38.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「只有這些」是指什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.71,0:08:41.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這裡只給品牌商品的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.78,0:08:46.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛  僅剩的錢都交出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.59,0:08:48.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須要帶獎品回去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.98,0:09:02.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小妹妹  一開始就瞄準價格高的可是不行的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.68,0:09:04.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可不是容易打落的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.08,0:09:06.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,價格很高嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.72,0:09:09.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一開始要瞄準那些容易打落的才行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.94,0:09:15.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,容易打落什麼的…剩下的就只有奶糖這個選項了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.40,0:09:28.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.35,0:09:30.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個奶糖的下面完全粘住了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.31,0:09:33.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}1英寸=1000密爾
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.31,0:09:33.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有幾密爾就打落了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.25,0:09:36.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小妹妹  你的素質可真好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.64,0:09:39.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非你是現役的槍手？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.75,0:09:40.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開個玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.36,0:09:49.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然這個茄子是紋絲不動
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.87,0:09:52.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了怎麼了  一副洩氣的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.68,0:09:55.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是  你該不會是在想我動了手腳了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.63,0:09:58.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我的店面看上去有點寒酸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.28,0:10:01.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,元氣滿滿和不作手腳是絕對可保證的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.20,0:10:06.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不  這個絕對是耍了什麼花招
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.96,0:10:25.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個是！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.96,0:10:29.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  那個那個  你看你看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.71,0:10:32.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,釘子啊  都能看到釘子了  釘子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.11,0:10:35.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不就是詐騙嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.85,0:10:40.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  你怎麼一句話都不說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.50,0:10:43.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說你這樣的是不行的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.91,0:10:46.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你剛才不是還挺有精神的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.33,0:10:49.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣看來  你也在奶糖下面耍了花招的吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.30,0:10:52.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為什麼要裝睡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.00,0:10:56.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還剩下一發子彈  我到底該瞄準哪個才好啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.74,0:11:26.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你別再來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.99,0:11:27.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這算什麼啊…
