Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.14,0:01:08.80,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}現在才第一次發覺到
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.80,0:01:11.51,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}我是不是墜入愛河了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.55,0:01:14.13,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}24小時滿腦子都是你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.15,0:01:15.91,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}意識不受控制
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.95,0:01:18.70,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}覺得與平時不同
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.64,0:01:17.55,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\an6}覺\N得
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.75,0:01:21.26,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}和你生硬的對話
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.29,0:01:20.27,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\an6}兩\N個\N人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.27,0:01:24.11,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}難道  不對  是單相思
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.88,0:01:22.99,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\an6}兩\N情\N相\N悅
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.15,0:01:26.48,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}糟了  視線和他對上了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.49,0:01:30.63,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}什麼什麼  這種忐忑心情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.78,0:01:36.14,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}思考回路亂成一團
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.44,0:01:42.43,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}那種事情  我可是第一次哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.08,0:01:46.45,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}感覺都要發燒了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.92,0:01:50.65,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}急轉直下的我的愛慕之情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.71,0:01:53.32,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}眨眼間  臉像著火般變得通紅
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.37,0:01:55.89,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}怎怎怎麼可能  我的手居然在顫抖
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.05,0:01:58.72,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}這是所謂的戀愛嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.79,0:02:01.22,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}不不不不好了  說話咬到舌頭了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.30,0:02:03.97,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}糟糕的沉默  我語無倫次
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.01,0:02:06.60,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}我想知道  你對我的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.50,0:02:05.19,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\an6}你\N對\N我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.65,0:02:09.17,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}單單單單☆單相思
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.49,0:02:12.41,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}初戀！  在平日的上學路上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.44,0:02:15.70,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}閃閃發光  I DO fall in love！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.83,0:02:18.43,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}好像能在天空飛翔般
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.50,0:02:21.55,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}單單單單☆單相思
